setting.name: HPAdjustedPrintQuality
HPPrintQuality
HPSelectedPhysicalPaperSizeIsRigid
setting.single-valid-value: true if HPSelectedPhysicalPaperSize in {rigid-8x10, rigid-5x7-13x18, rigid-13x19}; false otherwise;

setting.name: HPManualBorderless
HPManualBorderlessEnabledState
HPPaperType
setting.valid-values: *: (not HPPhysicalPaperSize has attribute "$Root/capabilities/constrained-media-types/disallowed-media-types[@name=$Self/disallowed-media-types/@ref-name]/reference[@name='%*%']") and (( HPPenConfigBlack in {true}) or (* has attribute "media-type-info/@black-only[.='true']"));

setting.name: HPPaperTypeSupportsBorderless
setting.single-valid-value: true if not Printer has attribute "$Root/capabilities/constrained-media-types/disallowed-media-types[@name='disallowed-media-borderless-types']/reference[@name='%HPPaperType%']"; false otherwise;

setting.name: HPAutoWidthSensor
HPPaperSource
setting.default-value: * if (HPPaperType has attribute "media-type-info/@default-paper-source[.='%*%']") or ((not HPPaperType has attribute "media-type-info/@default-paper-source") and (HPPhysicalPaperSize has attribute "default-media-source[.='%*%']")) or ((not HPPaperType has attribute "media-type-info/@default-paper-source") and (not HPPhysicalPaperSize has attribute "default-media-source") and (Printer has attribute "capabilities/media-source-pick/@default[.='%*%']"));
